  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "I can feel it, I can feel it from my head to my toes Why you don't know sin? Feeling so nice in this wild dream Reality as it seems Hand in hand we're walking through the flames Flames of our hearts desire Oh and you're looking so good It shows in my form, my tone Yeah I wanna get you all alone Oh you can waste my time anyways Just go slow, don't rush what this means I'm feeling it, I'm feeling it The bond between us, oh baby it comes fast And then all of a sudden your loving make it last But what do we do to make it past the old you All this new in front of you, what do you do? Oh God, I can't even explain the one I feel It's like it's something that can't be real Oh, hand in hand we're walking Fire lies, fire lies a battle we brought Oh, you go slow Till you feel it all, you just Understand the world when we walk And understand the way that we talk It's getting late And time for fighting, for living, for looking in As it goes away, time's direction For age, for loss, for confusion I don't even know where weapons come last Weapons come in a fight, it's war at last Like every other one Fighting for what's mine Fighting for what's yours It's just the way I guess we're raised, we can't control But we can If you just walk in my hand Oh yeah, we can Thanks for watching!",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 22.65999984741211,
      "text": "I can feel it, I can feel it from my head to my toes",
      "start": 14.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 27.68000030517578,
      "text": "Why you don't know sin?",
      "start": 23.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 33.65999984741211,
      "text": "Feeling so nice in this wild dream",
      "start": 29.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 39.439998626708984,
      "text": "Reality as it seems",
      "start": 34.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 44.65999984741211,
      "text": "Hand in hand we're walking through the flames",
      "start": 40.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 49.29999923706055,
      "text": "Flames of our hearts desire",
      "start": 45.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 56.540000915527344,
      "text": "Oh and you're looking so good",
      "start": 52.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 61.13999938964844,
      "text": "It shows in my form, my tone",
      "start": 57.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 66.30000305175781,
      "text": "Yeah I wanna get you all alone",
      "start": 62
    },
    {
      "end": 71.55999755859375,
      "text": "Oh you can waste my time anyways",
      "start": 67.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 82.4800033569336,
      "text": "Just go slow, don't rush what this means",
      "start": 71.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 88.63999938964844,
      "text": "I'm feeling it, I'm feeling it",
      "start": 83.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 94.55999755859375,
      "text": "The bond between us, oh baby it comes fast",
      "start": 88.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 100.72000122070312,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden your loving make it last",
      "start": 95.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 109.55999755859375,
      "text": "But what do we do to make it past the old you",
      "start": 101.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 115.55999755859375,
      "text": "All this new in front of you, what do you do?",
      "start": 110.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 123.05999755859375,
      "text": "Oh God, I can't even explain the one I feel",
      "start": 117.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 128.4199981689453,
      "text": "It's like it's something that can't be real",
      "start": 123.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 133.1199951171875,
      "text": "Oh, hand in hand we're walking",
      "start": 129.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 140.36000061035156,
      "text": "Fire lies, fire lies a battle we brought",
      "start": 134.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 146.72000122070312,
      "text": "Oh, you go slow",
      "start": 142.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 150.3000030517578,
      "text": "Till you feel it all, you just",
      "start": 147.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 153.22000122070312,
      "text": "Understand the world when we walk",
      "start": 150.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 156.05999755859375,
      "text": "And understand the way that we talk",
      "start": 153.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 158.24000549316406,
      "text": "It's getting late",
      "start": 156.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 163.25999450683594,
      "text": "And time for fighting, for living, for looking in",
      "start": 159.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 167.17999267578125,
      "text": "As it goes away, time's direction",
      "start": 163.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 169.94000244140625,
      "text": "For age, for loss, for confusion",
      "start": 167.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 174.05999755859375,
      "text": "I don't even know where weapons come last",
      "start": 169.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 179.77999877929688,
      "text": "Weapons come in a fight, it's war at last",
      "start": 174.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 183.05999755859375,
      "text": "Like every other one",
      "start": 180.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 186.05999755859375,
      "text": "Fighting for what's mine",
      "start": 184.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 189.25999450683594,
      "text": "Fighting for what's yours",
      "start": 186.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 191.36000061035156,
      "text": "It's just the way",
      "start": 189.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 194.8800048828125,
      "text": "I guess we're raised, we can't control",
      "start": 192.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 196.05999755859375,
      "text": "But we can",
      "start": 194.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 200.22000122070312,
      "text": "If you just walk in my hand",
      "start": 196.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 202.05999755859375,
      "text": "Oh yeah, we can",
      "start": 200.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 215.39999389648438,
      "text": "Thanks for watching!",
      "start": 215.32000732421875
    }
  ],
